1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,622
Welcome to the Cultivating Self Energy
Practice.

2
00:00:03,622 --> 00:00:09,170
This practice is an invitation to
strengthen your connection with the

3
00:00:09,170 --> 00:00:12,678
steady, compassionate center of your
system.

4
00:00:12,678 --> 00:00:20,261
Self-energy does not need to be forced.
It is not a performance. It is the part

5
00:00:20,261 --> 00:00:27,260
of you that can notice, listen, care, and
respond with more spaciousness.

6
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,464
Begin by finding a comfortable position.

7
00:00:30,464 --> 00:00:33,436
Let your body be supported.

8
00:00:33,436 --> 00:00:40,634
Let your eyes close if that feels okay,
or let your gaze rest softly.

9
00:00:40,634 --> 00:00:42,770
Take a slow breath in.

10
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:51,770
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:53,395
And let it out.

12
00:00:53,395 --> 00:00:55,485
Again, breathing in.

13
00:01:04,485 --> 00:01:04,485
<break time="3s" />

14
00:01:04,485 --> 00:01:06,668
And breathing out.

15
00:01:06,668 --> 00:01:09,640
Now notice what is present in your body.

16
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:16,171
You might notice tension, warmth,
numbness, movement, restlessness, or

17
00:01:16,171 --> 00:01:17,117
stillness.

18
00:01:17,117 --> 00:01:20,414
Whatever is here, simply notice it.

19
00:01:20,414 --> 00:01:23,386
Now bring your attention to your inner
world.

20
00:01:23,386 --> 00:01:28,680
Ask gently: What parts of me are active
right now?

21
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:40,680
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

22
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:43,048
Let the answer come slowly.

23
00:02:01,048 --> 00:02:01,048
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

24
00:02:01,048 --> 00:02:07,480
You may notice a manager part, a worried
part, a tired part, a protective part, a

25
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:13,591
younger part, a part that wants to do
this correctly, or a part that does not

26
00:02:13,591 --> 00:02:15,119
trust this process.

27
00:02:15,119 --> 00:02:17,720
Each one is welcome to be noticed.

28
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:21,714
Now ask: How do I feel toward the parts I
am noticing?

29
00:02:33,714 --> 00:02:33,714
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

30
00:02:33,714 --> 00:02:38,915
If you feel curiosity, compassion, or
calm, notice that.

31
00:02:38,915 --> 00:02:46,247
If you feel judgment, fear, pressure, or
impatience, notice that too. Those

32
00:02:46,247 --> 00:02:49,318
reactions may be parts as well.

33
00:02:49,318 --> 00:02:51,640
Nothing is wrong.

34
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:56,656
Take a moment to acknowledge any part
that is trying to manage this practice.

35
00:02:56,656 --> 00:03:03,984
You might say inside: I see you. You are
trying to help. You do not have to

36
00:03:03,984 --> 00:03:10,124
disappear. Would you be willing to give
me just a little space?

37
00:03:22,124 --> 00:03:22,124
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

38
00:03:22,124 --> 00:03:25,886
Now notice whether there is even a small
opening.

39
00:03:25,886 --> 00:03:33,595
A little space. A little breath. A little
softness. A little willingness.

40
00:03:33,595 --> 00:03:35,824
Let that be enough.

41
00:03:35,824 --> 00:03:39,818
Now we will gently invite the qualities
of Self-energy.

42
00:03:39,818 --> 00:03:41,211
Begin with calm.

43
00:03:41,211 --> 00:03:46,552
Ask: Where is calm, even one percent,
available right now?

44
00:03:58,552 --> 00:03:58,552
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

45
00:03:58,552 --> 00:04:04,197
Maybe in your breath. Maybe in your
hands. Maybe in the space around your

46
00:04:04,197 --> 00:04:04,589
body.

47
00:04:04,589 --> 00:04:06,261
Now curiosity.

48
00:04:06,261 --> 00:04:12,401
Ask: Can I be interested in what is
happening inside without needing to fix

49
00:04:12,401 --> 00:04:13,645
it immediately?

50
00:04:25,645 --> 00:04:25,645
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

51
00:04:25,645 --> 00:04:27,410
Now compassion.

52
00:04:27,410 --> 00:04:32,631
Ask: Can I sense that these parts are
trying to help me, even when their

53
00:04:32,631 --> 00:04:34,469
strategies are difficult?

54
00:04:46,469 --> 00:04:46,469
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

55
00:04:46,469 --> 00:04:47,444
Now clarity.

56
00:04:47,444 --> 00:04:53,388
Ask: What do I understand a little more
clearly about my inner world right now?

57
00:05:05,388 --> 00:05:05,388
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

58
00:05:05,388 --> 00:05:07,013
Now courage.

59
00:05:07,013 --> 00:05:12,029
Ask: What is brave about being present
with myself today?

60
00:05:24,029 --> 00:05:24,029
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

61
00:05:24,029 --> 00:05:25,283
Now confidence.

62
00:05:25,283 --> 00:05:31,599
Ask: Can I trust that I can listen
slowly, one step at a time?

63
00:05:43,599 --> 00:05:43,599
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

64
00:05:43,599 --> 00:05:44,853
Now creativity.

65
00:05:44,853 --> 00:05:50,333
Ask: Is there another way to be with this
that my system has not tried yet?

66
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:02,333
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

67
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:04,191
Now connectedness.

68
00:06:04,191 --> 00:06:11,096
Ask: Can I sense connection to my body,
my breath, this moment, or the parts of

69
00:06:11,096 --> 00:06:12,690
me that need care?

70
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:24,690
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

71
00:06:24,690 --> 00:06:28,870
Now choose one Self quality that feels
most available.

72
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:32,167
Let that quality become a gentle
presence.

73
00:06:32,167 --> 00:06:38,715
Not a force. Not a command. Just a warmth
or spaciousness near you.

74
00:06:38,715 --> 00:06:43,823
Now ask: Which part of me most needs this
quality today?

75
00:06:55,823 --> 00:06:55,823
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

76
00:06:55,823 --> 00:06:59,863
Let one part come forward if it wants to.

77
00:06:59,863 --> 00:07:01,628
Notice it gently.

78
00:07:01,628 --> 00:07:05,808
Where is it? How close is it? What does
it seem to need?

79
00:07:17,808 --> 00:07:17,808
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

80
00:07:17,808 --> 00:07:20,641
Offer the Self quality to this part.

81
00:07:20,641 --> 00:07:24,728
If calm is present, let calm be near it.

82
00:07:24,728 --> 00:07:29,186
If compassion is present, let compassion
surround it.

83
00:07:29,186 --> 00:07:34,805
If curiosity is present, let curiosity
listen.

84
00:07:52,805 --> 00:07:52,805
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

85
00:07:52,805 --> 00:07:56,613
If courage is present, let courage help
you stay.

86
00:07:56,613 --> 00:08:03,308
You might say: I am here with you. I want
to understand. You do not have to carry

87
00:08:03,308 --> 00:08:05,065
this alone right now.

88
00:08:14,065 --> 00:08:14,065
<break time="3s" />

89
00:08:14,065 --> 00:08:16,712
Notice how the part responds.

90
00:08:34,712 --> 00:08:34,712
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

91
00:08:34,712 --> 00:08:40,053
It does not have to transform. It does
not have to trust you completely.

92
00:08:40,053 --> 00:08:42,514
A small shift is enough.

93
00:08:42,514 --> 00:08:47,437
Now ask this part: What do you want me to
remember after this practice?

94
00:08:59,437 --> 00:08:59,437
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

95
00:08:59,437 --> 00:09:00,552
Listen.

96
00:09:18,552 --> 00:09:18,552
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

97
00:09:18,552 --> 00:09:22,871
Now thank the part for whatever it shared
or did not share.

98
00:09:22,871 --> 00:09:26,447
Thank your system for allowing this much
contact.

99
00:09:26,447 --> 00:09:28,397
Take a slow breath in.

100
00:09:37,397 --> 00:09:37,397
<break time="3s" />

101
00:09:37,397 --> 00:09:38,790
And let it out.

102
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:41,530
Bring your attention back to your body.

103
00:09:41,530 --> 00:09:44,595
Feel the support underneath you.

104
00:09:56,595 --> 00:09:56,595
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

105
00:09:56,595 --> 00:09:58,778
Notice the room around you.

106
00:10:07,778 --> 00:10:07,778
<break time="3s" />

107
00:10:07,778 --> 00:10:13,537
Before you finish, name one Self-energy
quality you want to practice today.

108
00:10:13,537 --> 00:10:16,231
When you are ready, gently return.

109
00:10:16,231 --> 00:10:21,508
Carry these qualities like a lantern
within you. It does not need to shine

110
00:10:21,508 --> 00:10:27,292
brightly all the time. Even a faint light
can help a part know that you are here,

111
00:10:27,292 --> 00:10:30,256
listening, and willing to lead with care.

